    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a thrilling 2D  adventure as Sam, a spirited young farmer. His peaceful life is shattered when a shadowy entity abducts his beloved Grandpa, whisking him away into the mystical Bamboo Forest. Now, Sam must embrace his destiny and become a true Master of Bushido to rescue his family and uncover the secrets lurking within the forest's depths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience fast-paced 2D side-scrolling action with finely-tuned melee combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle a wacky cast of enemies, each with their own unique attack patterns and weaknesses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twenty-nine unique hand crafted levels for you to unlock and play, each designed with their own perils and challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn &quot;Bamboo Coins&quot; by chopping bamboo. Spend your hard-earned currency in the shop to unlock a variety of cosmetic and functional upgrades including stylish new outfits with unique weapon skins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy your adventure with 32 fully steam integrated and challenging achievements to unlock.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive the challenges presented in each unique level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use power-ups to boost your ability and protect yourself from hazards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a hand-drawn world brought to life with traditional 2D frame-by-frame animation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of the katana and unleash your inner warrior, become the Master of Bushido.</p></li></ul>",
